  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "2005-03-02", 
    "text": "Ombudsman Reauthorization Act of 2005 - Amends the Solid Waste Disposal Act to reestablish the Office of the Ombudsman within the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA). Specifies the Ombudsman's duties and authorities. Requires the Ombudsman to appoint a Deputy Ombudsman for each EPA region. Provides employee protections for persons complying with this Act."
  }, 
